        "image_with_text_7tTYyw": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Ring_c9fca542-7476-4257-97b3-4a6a338a7b93.jpg",
            "text": "<p>One of the most striking aspects of this trend is that jewelry is not just restricted to grand occasions such as black-tie events. As a part of daily wear, evergreen accessories such as diamond studs, stackable rings women and pendant chains are embraced as a part of daily elegance. </p>",
