            "text": "<p>Certain designs become the focal point of a look. Gold threader <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Earrings\">earrings</a> and women <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Necklaces\">necaklaces</a> look chic. They are becoming a popular self-gifting choice, and a woman’s companion for dinners, parties, and even office presentations.</p>",
