          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> These bold pieces express confidence and individuality, allowing women to make a lasting impression wherever they go. With unique craftsmanship and modern aesthetics, statement jewelry truly celebrates personal style and empowerment.</p>",
