            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bespoke_2d98d921-dee8-47f6-9a88-dfcbe48f105f.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Nothing feels more intimate than personalized jewelry. Women are choosing jewelry that feels more personal, versatile and timeless. Custom engravings and initials on diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rings\">rings</a> for women make the piece even more unique and special. </p>",
