        "rich_text_D9Uj7r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>The trend of self gifting signals evolution. Women are no longer waiting to be adorned by others, but choosing pieces that celebrate their own stories. Jewelry is crafted with this mindset in mind to create pieces that feel personal, balance wearability and radiate luxury. Diamond jewelry embodies elegance and Lab Grown Diamond price makes this beauty more accessible while also choosing conscious luxury. Choosing jewelry for yourself is not just a purchase, but an act of self love, a celebration of your journey, and precious moments carved into gold and gemstones.  </p>",
